{"page_content": "![](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/_assets/3137b1a864c689786cac76b3def62dd1/Assets/img/default-banner.jpg)\n\n# Driving Course\n\nThe SAAQ oversees the contents of the driving courses (SAAQ road safety education programs). It recognizes schools that can offer driving courses for the purposes of obtaining a driver's licence. It also supports students should their driving school close, be sold, or have its recognition revoked. The SAAQ also processes complaints received regarding driving schools.\n\n## Driving schools recognized by the SAAQ\n\nOnly driving schools recognized by the SAAQ offer the programs that are mandatory for obtaining a driver's licence. [Find a recognized driving school](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/driving-course/finding-recognized-driving-school).\n\nLearn more about the duration and structure of the different driving courses. Consult learning material as well as useful exercises.\n\nLast update: November 5, 2025\n\n- ## See also\n\n[Obtaining a Driver's Licence](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/drivers-licences/obtaining-licence/passenger-vehicle-class-5)\n\n## Safety first, on the road and online\n\nWe are committed to protecting your personal information and privacy. That's why, when we collect data, we follow a [Policy on Privacy](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/policies/privacy) that is responsible and transparent. By continuing to browse without modifying your preferences, you accept the use of cookies.\n\nEdit settingsAcceptReject\n\nDétection du zoom", "metadata": {"title": "Driving Course - SAAQ", "description": "To drive a car in Québec, individuals must take a driving course and pass the SAAQ's tests.", "url": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/driving-course", "language": "en", "keywords": "Driving course, knowledge test, road test, driver's licence, exercises, practice for the test, passing the test", "robots": null, "og_title": "Driving Course", "og_description": "To drive a car in Québec, individuals must take a driving course and pass the